TRAVEL INSURANCE.

This refers to the type of insurance that covers the loss and costs associated with travelling. It’s a useful protection especially for those going abroad. It is intended to cover medical expenses, trip cancellations, lost luggage, flight accidents and other losses occurred during travelling. It is designed to provide financial protection for unexpected events that impact a traveler’s trip.

Common forms of Travel Insurance;
Single trip travel insurance,
Annual travel insurance,
Group travel insurance.

Benefits of travel insurance,
It enables the passenger to receive treatment from other countries.
It helps the passenger to travel with all heath documents.
Helps the passenger to know his/her health status.


